'''叠氮甲烷'''（CH<sub>3</sub>N<sub>3</sub>）是{{le|烷基叠氮化物|Alkyl azides}}的一种，它们都属于[[叠氮酸|叠氮酸]]的共价型衍生物。叠氮甲烷是一种直线型分子。根据[[共振式|共振式]]，中间的氮原子的两对成键电子显然是直线形排列的，但与甲基相连的氮原子却有三对孤对电子：H<sub>3</sub>C-N=N<sup>+</sup>=N<sup>-</sup> ⇔ H<sub>3</sub>C-N<sup>-</sup>-N<sup>+</sup>≡N 。<ref> [[Linus_Pauling|Pauling, Linus]], Brockway, O.; The Adjacent Charge Rule and the Structure of Methyl Azide, [[Methyl_nitrate|Methyl nitrate]], and [[Fluorine_nitrate|Fluorine nitrate]]; [[Journal_of_the_American_Chemical_Society|JACS]], 1937, 59 (1), pp 13-20 DOI:10.1021/ja01280a005 </ref>

它可以由[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]的[[甲基化|甲基化]]反应制得。该物质最早于1905年制得。<ref> Dimroth, O. and Wislicenus, W.; [[Chemische_Berichte|Chemische Berichte]] ; 38, 1573 (1905) </ref>
它以如下的[[反应级数|一级反应]]分解：CH<sub>3</sub>N<sub>3</sub> → CH<sub>3</sub>N + N<sub>2</sub>。<ref>O'Dell, M.S. and Darwent B. [http://article.pubs.nrc-cnrc.gc.ca/ppv/RPViewDoc?issn=1480-3291&volume=48&issue=7&startPage=1140 Thermal decomposition of methyl azide]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}[[Canadian_Journal_of_Chemistry|Canadian Journal of Chemistry]], 48, 1140 (1970) </ref>

[[无生源论|无生源论]]认为，叠氮甲烷可能是在[[星际冰|星际冰]]中由高能[[银河宇宙射线|银河宇宙射线]]和[[光子|光子]]合成分子的前体之一。<ref>Alfredo Quinto-Hernandez and Alec M. Wodtke, Department of Chemistry and Biochemistry, [[University_of_California,_Santa_Barbara|University of California, Santa Barbara]]; Chris J. Bennett, Y. Seol Kim, and Ralf I. Kaiser; Department of Chemistry, [[University_of_Hawaii_at_Manoa|University of Hawaii at Manoa]]; 

[http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jp103028v On the Interaction of Methyl Azide (CH3N3) Ices with Ionizing Radiation: Formation of Methanimine (CH2NH), Hydrogen Cyanide (HCN), and Hydrogen Isocyanide (HNC)] {{Wayback|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jp103028v |date=20200131191102 }} ; [[Journal_of_Physical_Chemistry|Journal of Physical Chemistry]]
DOI: 10.1021/jp103028v  Publication Date (Web): December 17, 2010</ref>

== 安全措施 ==
叠氮甲烷在常温时稳定但加热时可能[[爆炸|爆炸]]。<ref> Bretherick's handbook of reactive chemical hazards; edited by P. G. Urben </ref>  汞的存在将增加它对震动和火花的敏感度。它与[[丙二酸二甲酯|丙二酸二甲酯]]、[[甲醇钠|甲醇钠]]、[[汞|汞]]、[[甲醇|甲醇]]、[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]、[[硫酸二甲酯|硫酸二甲酯]]、[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]、[[叠氮酸|叠氮酸]]不能共存。加热分解时产生有毒的[[氮氧化物|氮氧化物]]气体。{{cn}}它可以在-80℃的黑暗中无限期储存。<ref name="e-EROS">{{Citation|last=Chae|first=Junghyun|title=Methyl Azide|date=2008-03-14|encyclopedia=Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis|pages=rn00795|editor-last=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|place=Chichester, UK|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|language=en|doi=10.1002/047084289x.rn00795|isbn=978-0-471-93623-7}}</ref>

